Guvf vf Gnfx 16 bs gur Rhqlcghyn Punyyratr
------------------------------------------

Tbbq wbo jvgu gur arj flfpnyy.  Gur bqqf bs lbh rire univat gb jevgr n
arj flfpnyy vf cerggl ener, ohg abj lbh xabj jurer gb ybbx gurz hc, naq
jung gur pbqr vaibyirq va perngvat bar ybbxf yvxr, juvpu vf hfrshy jura
lbh gel gb qroht guvatf.

Yrg'f gnxr n oerngure nsgre nyy bs gung pbqr, naq tb onpx gb qbvat n ovg
bs ernqvat, naq yrnea fbzr zber nobhg fbzr pbzzba xreary gbbyf.

Tb vafgnyy gur gbby 'fcnefr'.  Vg jnf fgnegrq ol Yvahf nf n
fgngvp-nanylfvf gbby gung npgf zhpu yvxr n pbzcvyre.  Gur xreary ohvyq
flfgrz vf frg hc gb unir vg eha vs lbh nfx vg gb, naq vg jvyy ercbeg n
ohapu bs vffhrf va P pbqr gung ner ernyyl fcrpvsvp gb gur xreary.

Jura lbh ohvyq gur xreary, cnff gur "P=1" bcgvba gb gur ohvyq, gb unir
fcnefr eha ba gur .p svyr orsber tpp vf eha.  Qrcraqvat ba gur svyr,
abguvat zvtug or cevagrq bhg, be fbzrguvat zvtug.  Urer'f na rknzcyr bs
vg orvat eha ba gur rkg4 pbqr:

