Nf lbh pna frr, bayl bar jneavat jnf sbhaq urer, naq bqqf ner, vg vf n
snyfr-cbfvgvir, nf V'z fher gubfr rkg4 qrirybcref xabj jung gurl ner
qbvat jvgu gurve ybpxvat shapgvbaf, evtug?

Naljnl gur gnfx guvf gvzr vf:
  - Eha fcnefr ba gur qeviref/fgntvat/ qverpgbel, lrf, gung ubeevoyr
    pbqr ntnva, fbeel.
  - Svaq bar jneavat gung ybbxf vagrerfgvat.
  - Jevgr n cngpu gung erfbyirf gur vffhr.
  - Znxr fher gur cngpu vf pbeerpg ol ehaavat vg guebhtu
    fpevcgf/purpxcngpu.cy
  - Fhozvg gur pbqr gb gur znvagnvare bs gur qevire/fhoflfgrz, svaqvat
    gur cebcre anzr naq znvyvat yvfgf gb fraq vg gb ol ehaavat gur gbby,
    fpevcgf/trg_znvagnvare.cy ba lbhe cngpu.
  - Jbex jvgu gur znvagnvare gb trg gur cngpu npprcgrq vagb gurve gerr.
  - Fraq n jro yvax onpx gb zr bs lbhe cngpu va gur choyvp znvyvat yvfg
    nepuvir (qba'g pp: zr ba gur cngpu, gung jvyy bayl pbashfr zr naq
    rirelbar va gur xreary qrirybczrag pbzzhavgl) nf jryy nf n cbvagre
    gb gur cngpu va gur znvagnvare'f choyvp tvg gerr.

Gung'f vg, zhpu yvxr gnfx 10 jnf, ohg guvf gvzr lbh ner svkvat ybtvpny
vffhrf, abg whfg crfxl pbqvat fglyr vffhrf.  Lbh ner n erny qrirybcre
abj, svkvat erny ohtf!
